Altium Documentation
To follow my own flow of learning Altium through this project and the process of using Alitum to create this PCB.

Altium Schematic
Panels > Explorer
pick component
  -right click on component > place
     -left click to place
     -right click to leave place command
     
[Understanding Voltage for Power Supply]

When picking a component to use, check the tolerance/ package size (imperial)
    -space key = rotate

Resistors footprints:
  red side is the positive side and is always towards the side recieving power.
  
Right click anywhere > place > wire > right click to leave tool
